Quote:  <i>Berm</i>- 1. Continuous horizontal bench (or benches) cut into a a batter to ensure slope stability. 2. Narrow strip of land separating footpath from carriageway or between footpath and boundary of road reserve used for underground services, and often widened to include planning.
